1157
01:26:20,883 --> 01:26:23,408
only you're the same as you were, too...

1158
01:26:23,720 --> 01:26:26,985
so l guess things
will never be the same again.

1159
01:26:34,897 --> 01:26:36,330
Good night.

1160
01:26:46,375 --> 01:26:48,570
-Got caught in the door.
