l was trying to stop it.

1164
01:28:33,616 --> 01:28:35,379
Well, there it goes again.

1165
01:28:52,635 --> 01:28:54,865
You're all confused, aren't you?

1166
01:28:56,606 --> 01:28:58,267
-Aren't you?
