No more doubts? No more being....

1178
01:29:28,938 --> 01:29:30,963
-Except....
-Except what?

1179
01:29:31,507 --> 01:29:34,499
-There's only one thing that bothers me.
-What?

1180
01:29:37,013 --> 01:29:38,605
This darn lock.

1181
